snippet.title: Mega-CD Longplay [048] The Lawnmower Man
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: MadMatty

This is a puzzle game held togetehr by fmv clips from the movie of the same name. Not great but ok for one playthrough.

The death right at the start of the game was intentional in order to show this game over anim. -
